summary:
This is a small mod that I made because I didn\'t like any of the other player homes.
I tend to collect things, and nothing I could find could display my collection properly.
descriptionHtml:
Since this is my first mod, and I\'m learning I\'ll be updating this regularly.
If you find anything wrong, or know how to fix some things I don\'t don\'t hesitate to let me know.

I\'ll update this to show what I\'ve fixed in the future.
author: Grendo
